channel.title: [REQ] Website Template
channel.description:
This might be a big project, so I'm only looking for advanced people who can do professional website templates using Photoshop.
I don't need the template in HTML, I just need 1 template (the index). I'm going to try and show you what I want: [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img251.imageshack.us/img251/4923/dvsup6.jpg[/img][/URL]
I want buttons on the nav column, not just text links. I need about 7 of them. The buttons need to be sleek and stylish, along with everything else.
Ask any questions you may have. I don't expect you to do this in a few hours. I'm willing to wait a couple of weeks. Once you are done, let me know.
beyond_mexico@hotmail.co.uk
I'll try and come up with a reward for you. I'll also make sure you get the graphics award ;)
<3 you all
